@startuml FUSE挂载VFS完整时序
box 内核模块初始化阶段
participant Kernel_Init as "fuse.ko模块加载"
end box

box 用户态LibFUSE进程
participant LibFUSE as "libfuse(ulogfs进程)"
end box

box Linux VFS虚拟文件系统
participant VFS as "VFS层"
end box

box FUSE内核驱动
participant FUSE_KO as "fuse.ko驱动\n/dev/fuse字符设备"
end box

note over Kernel_Init,FUSE_KO
阶段1：内核模块初始化，向VFS注册FUSE文件系统、注册/dev/fuse字符设备
end note

Kernel_Init->VFS: fuse_fs_register() 注册FUSE文件系统类型\n绑定super/inode/file三套VFS操作表
Kernel_Init->FUSE_KO: misc_register() 注册/dev/fuse字符设备驱动

note over LibFUSE,FUSE_KO
阶段2：用户态打开/dev/fuse获取通信fd
end note
LibFUSE->FUSE_KO: open("/dev/fuse", O_RDWR)
activate FUSE_KO
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 分配struct fuse_dev，预留通信绑定位置
FUSE_KO-->LibFUSE: 返回通信fd=3
deactivate FUSE_KO

note over LibFUSE,VFS
阶段3：用户态调用mount系统调用，发起VFS挂载
end note
LibFUSE->VFS: mount("fuse","/mnt/ulogfs", fd=3, rootmode, uid, gid)
activate VFS
VFS->FUSE_KO: 调用fuse_get_tree() 进入FUSE挂载逻辑
deactivate VFS

note over VFS,FUSE_KO
阶段4：初始化超级块、fuse_mount、fuse_conn通信通道
end note
activate FUSE_KO
FUSE_KO->VFS: 分配struct super_block
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 分配struct fuse_mount，sb->s_fs_info = fuse_mount
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 分配全局唯一struct fuse_conn通信对象\n初始化pending/processing/io三大请求队列
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 绑定/dev/fuse内核file与fuse_conn
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 创建根目录fuse_inode(nodeid=1)，挂载VFS根dentry
deactivate FUSE_KO

note over FUSE_KO,LibFUSE
阶段5：FUSE_INIT协议握手，协商零拷贝等能力
end note

FUSE_KO->LibFUSE: /dev/fuse下发FUSE_INIT握手请求(协议版本、内核能力)

activate LibFUSE
LibFUSE->FUSE_KO: 返回握手应答(支持FUSE_CAP_SPLICE_READ、协议版本)
deactivate LibFUSE

activate FUSE_KO
FUSE_KO->FUSE_KO: 更新fuse_conn协议、能力位，标记连接已就绪
deactivate FUSE_KO

note over VFS,LibFUSE
阶段6：挂载完成，VFS接管挂载点，FUSE正式接入VFS
end note
VFS->VFS: 将根dentry绑定到/mnt/ulogfs挂载点
LibFUSE->FUSE_KO: 循环阻塞read(/dev/fuse)，等待VFS下发文件系统请求

note over VFS,FUSE_KO
后续所有/mnt/ulogfs下的open/read/write系统调用\n都会经VFS路由到fuse.ko，封装请求下发用户态
end note
@enduml